data.description: Tidy Three Bedroom, One Full Bath Ranch is ready for you! Perfect Starter home or Investment Property. ALL VINYL Siding. Covered Front Porch. Some Updates Include: Roof Approximately 2020, Water Softener 2022, Hot Water Heater 2023. Offering 1,108 Square Feet of Living Space per PRC. Cozy Living Room welcomes you as you enter the home. Living Room Leads to the Large UPDATED Kitchen that offers a Breakfast Bar, Ample Cabinets, Appliances; Plenty of space for a small dining room table, leading to the Laundry Room and Small Addition that includes a Separate Utility Room! Outside you can enjoy the Fenced Yard; Extended Driveway leads to a Large Two Car Detached Garage with One Opener, Workshop Area, plenty of off-street parking and Side Access Door. This Home is located within minutes to WPAFB, WSU, Schools, Parks, Highway Access and more. Fireplace is inoperable. Easy to Show, Priced to Sell Now!
